The paper deals with the problem of video retrieval, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also involves natural language processing (cs.CL) as it deals with queries described in natural language text. Additionally, the paper uses deep learning techniques (cs.MM) and proposes a new network architecture, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG).
